### Recorder data (data/recorder/ is portable; per-account/sensitive files are NOT) ###
# data/recorder/ is the committed snapshot of ~/.runelite/recorder/ minus
# anything per-account or sensitive. These patterns prevent the sync workflow
# from accidentally staging account-scoped files. See scripts/sync-recorder-data.sh.
data/recorder/sessions/
data/recorder/inspect/
data/recorder/login-state.json
data/recorder/widget-dump-*
# Per-account hashed files (filename is a 64-char hex hash of the account name)
data/recorder/buy-limits/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f]*
data/recorder/training-plans/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f]*
# Backup files / atomic-write temp files
data/recorder/**/*.bak
data/recorder/**/*.tmp
data/recorder/**/*.json.tmp